# A human assigned name for the resource. All resources SHOULD have a name, but the name may be extracted from the resource (e.g. ValueSet.name).
#: ImplementationGuide.definition.resource.name
msgid "CDS Bundle Response Recherche Profile"
msgstr "CDS Bundle Search Response Profile"

# A description of the reason that a resource has been included in the implementation guide.
#: ImplementationGuide.definition.resource.description
msgid "Profil « Bundle » de type « searchset » encapsulant une collection de 0, une ou plusieurs ressources « CareTeam » répondant aux critères de recherche. Les ressources référencées par les ressources CareTeam retournées sont aussi dans le Bundle s’il a été demandé de les inclure dans la requête GET."
msgstr "Bundle profile of type \"searchset\" encapsulating a collection of 0, 1 or more \"CareTeam\" resources that meet the search criteria. The resources referenced by the returned CareTeam resources are also in the Bundle if it was requested to include them in the GET request."

# A human assigned name for the resource. All resources SHOULD have a name, but the name may be extracted from the resource (e.g. ValueSet.name).
#: ImplementationGuide.definition.resource.name
msgid "CDS Bundle Transaction Creation Profile"
msgstr "CDS Bundle Transaction Creation Profile"

# A description of the reason that a resource has been included in the implementation guide.
#: ImplementationGuide.definition.resource.description
msgid "Profil défini dans le volet de Gestion du Cercle de Soins (flux 1c) pour créer un cercle de soins selon l’option Transaction.
Il s'agit d'un bundle de type `transaction` permettant d'organiser le contenu du flux de création d'un cercle de soins."
msgstr "Profile defined in the Circle of Care Management section (flow 1c) to create a circle of care according to the Transaction option.
This is a bundle of type `transaction` that allows organizing the content of the flow to create a circle of care."

# A human assigned name for the resource. All resources SHOULD have a name, but the name may be extracted from the resource (e.g. ValueSet.name).
#: ImplementationGuide.definition.resource.name
msgid "CDS Bundle Transaction MAJ Profile"
msgstr "CDS Bundle Transaction Update Profile"

# A description of the reason that a resource has been included in the implementation guide.
#: ImplementationGuide.definition.resource.description
msgid "Profil défini dans le volet de Gestion du Cercle de Soins (flux 1c) pour mettre à jour un cercle de soins selon l’option Transaction.
Il s'agit d'un bundle de type \"transaction\" permettant d'organiser le contenu du flux de création d'un cercle de soins."
msgstr "Profile defined in the Circle of Care Management section (flow 1c) to update a circle of care according to the Transaction option.
This is a bundle of type \"transaction\" that allows organizing the content of the flow to create a circle of care."

